				<td colspan="2"><span>Are there really no other songs or items that can be used by a bard to cure poison/disease/curse spells if a person doesn't own LoY expansion?
<br />

<br />
All other LoY class spells i'd seen before appeared to just be lesser versions of existing higher level spells, to fill in the gap between levels for some good abilities.  The aria line of cure songs seem to be invaluable though! I can't believe they never added upgrades to them in further expansions.
<br />

<br />
 Guess i've finally found a truly good reason for purchasing LoY after all of this time <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
